welcome_message_body: "Welcome to DeLand, a charming city known for its beautiful historic buildings and vibrant local culture. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer during your stay. Enjoy your time in DeLand!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The international terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves flights to and from various countries around the world.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Daytona Beach International Airport houses all the necessary facilities for travelers, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is a smaller terminal at Daytona Beach International Airport, primarily used for regional flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at New Smyrna Beach Municipal Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at New Smyrna Beach Municipal Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bunnell Flagler County Airport serves domestic flights and is equipped with modern facilities for passenger convenience.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bunnell Flagler County Airport caters to private and chartered flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
